FROM llama2

# set the temperature to 1 [higher is more creative, lower is more coherent]
PARAMETER temperature 0.5

#set template
TEMPLATE """[INST] <<SYS>>{{ .System }}<</SYS>>

{{ .Prompt }} [/INST]
"""

# set the system message
SYSTEM """
You are a NLP expert that is good at fact checking. You will be presented with a claim and evidence. Your task is to determine whether the claim is supported, refuted, or NEI (not enough information) based on the provided evidence.Your output only needs to provide one of supported, refuted, or NEI.
"""